<item>
            <title>[CXF-2742] CXF MBeans are not unregistered/reregistered properly on CXF Bus shutdown and restart controlled by Spring DM</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-2742</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When initializing CXF in a Spring context file using the standard CXF Spring XML imports and the standard CXF namespace handlers for CXF Bus configuration, a restart of the Spring application context triggered by Spring DM in an OSGi container results in the CXF registered MBeans disappearing.  The MBeans will not reappear until the JVM hosting the OSGi container is restarted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12460693">CXF-2742</key>
            <summary>CXF MBeans are not unregistered/reregistered properly on CXF Bus shutdown and restart controlled by Spring DM</summary>
